OL,4,Cretired teacher, 75, in catfishing plot
OL,6,FMcNaughton first met the retired
OL,7,FFettes College teacher online in 2021
OL,8,Fand proceeded to steal tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds from him after
OL,10,Fgaining access to his bank accounts.
OL,12,FWhen Mr Coshan found out about the
OL,13,Fthefts, he threatened to go to the
OL,14,Fpolice unless McNaughton provided him
OL,15,Fwith free sexual favours.
OL,17,FMcNaughton hatched a plot to kill the
OL,18,Fretired teacher after becoming "fed
OL,19,Fup" with the situation.
