OL,3,CLife behind bars for man who murdered
OL,4,Cretired teacher, 75, in catfishing plot
OL,6,FFollowing the killing, McNaughton,
OL,7,Falong with his flatmate Paul Black,
OL,8,F65, of Edinburgh, hid the pensioner's
OL,9,Fbody until about 15 August, when they
OL,10,Fput it in a suitcase and drove it to a
OL,11,Flayby on the A696, between Otterburn
OL,12,Fand Belsay, in Northumberland, where
OL,13,Fthey dumped it next to a wall.
OL,15,FMcNaughton admitted murder and
OL,16,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,17,Fjustice in 2023 before Black's trial.
