OL,6,FHe was sentenced to life imprisonment
OL,7,Fwith a recommendation that he serve a
OL,8,Fminimum of 22 years behind bars when
OL,9,Fhe was sentenced at Glasgow High Court
OL,10,Fon Monday (17 June).
OL,12,FBlack was cleared of murder following
OL,13,Fa trial at the High Court in Edinburgh
OL,14,Fin May, with the jury returning a not
OL,15,Fproven verdict.
OL,17,FHowever, during the trial, he admitted
OL,18,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,19,Fjustice for which he was sentenced to
OL,20,Ffive and a half years.
